data.description: Spacious three bedroom and two bath home, with spectacular views of the Columbia River! Desirable one level living, easy to maintain. Neutral color pallet through out. Ample windows throughout offering tons of natural lighting. Detached two car carport, with additional side parking. Large fully fenced backyard with plenty of room for relaxation.
